 & photos from Zimbabwe and many more!\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2922, \"end\": 2930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"score\": 0.9999999839219528, \"rank\": 1.1066124012977249e-08, \"text\": \"Zimbabwe\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the latest news\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"your addiction\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2894}, {\"ngram\": \"stories\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2916}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9NewZimbabwe.com.\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}]}"